metadata.name: FUTURE OF WORK BY ACHTZIG20
metadata.description:
The Future Of Work Tour by Achtzig20 and Vitra is an exclusive exploration format about finding answers on questions like: how is the future of work going to look like? how will our offices and spaces be like? how are we going to collaborate with each other?

By being a member of the FOW community you will be granted access to latest insights, recent research insights and inspiring impulses.

For more information follow achtzig20 and get in contact with us.
